00061 MTKt_status MtkReadData(
00062   const char *filename,     
00063   const char *gridname,     
00064   const char *fieldname,    
00065   MTKt_Region region,       
00066   MTKt_DataBuffer *databuf, 
00067   MTKt_MapInfo *mapinfo      )
00068 {
00069   MTKt_status status_code;  /* Return status code for error macros */
00070   MTKt_status status;       /* Return status */
00071   int32 fid = FAIL;     /* HDF-EOS File id */
00072   intn hdfstatus;       /* HDF return status */
00073 
00074   if (filename == NULL) return MTK_NULLPTR;
00075 
00076   /* Open file. */
00077   fid = GDopen((char*)filename, DFACC_READ);
00078   if (fid == FAIL) MTK_ERR_CODE_JUMP(MTK_HDFEOS_GDOPEN_FAILED);
00079 
00080   /* Read data. */
00081   status = MtkReadDataFid(fid, gridname, fieldname, region, databuf, mapinfo);
00082   MTK_ERR_COND_JUMP(status);
00083 
00084   /* Close file. */
00085   hdfstatus = GDclose(fid);
00086   if (hdfstatus == FAIL) MTK_ERR_CODE_JUMP(MTK_HDFEOS_GDCLOSE_FAILED);
00087   fid = FAIL;
00088 
00089   return MTK_SUCCESS;
00090 
00091  ERROR_HANDLE:
00092   if (fid != FAIL) GDclose(fid);
00093   return status_code;
00094 }
